metadata.shopMessage: **Vibrant and Colourful** or Muted and Dark? Choose from a variety of amazing icon designs by the best creators out there! There is something available for everyone. Most icon packs include alternatives and icon overlays. Use ShowAE to apply them!
metadata.shortcutsMessage: **Explore** the Show shortcuts below. ShowLive & SL App Helper shortcuts are required to install themes with this app. Install and setup ShowLive first before downloading themes.
metadata.howToMessage: **Follow our tutorials** and learn how to select, download and apply themes with ShowLive. We cover everything to get you started with easy to follow videos and detailed step by step written instructions. For further support visit our #Show Discord Server. Link at the bottom of this page.

metadata.downloadInstructionsMessage:
#Once download finishes:

Share the theme file to the SL Installer Shortcut to install the theme. Run the ShowLive Shortcut to apply the theme on your device.
